<div class="content" name="EntryHeader" uuid="629d4c21-91df-48dd-92ca-b150832da051"><p>The EntryHeader structure is used to describe an opaque array
of bytes associated with a <a href="ba4c4d80-ef81-49b4-848f-9714d72b5c01#gt_dc143034-cb8f-4d90-87ef-0fa96333807f" data-linktype="relative-path">context
property</a> within the context <a href="ba4c4d80-ef81-49b4-848f-9714d72b5c01#gt_aae39d05-becf-4cb4-bdfc-b05bc8ccabde" data-linktype="relative-path">ORPC extension</a>.</p><p>All fields MUST be marshaled with the same endianness as the
encompassing <a href="ba4c4d80-ef81-49b4-848f-9714d72b5c01#gt_8a7f6700-8311-45bc-af10-82e10accd331" data-linktype="relative-path">RPC</a> PDU.</p><table>
